---
import TestPage from "../layouts/TestPage.astro";
---

<TestPage
  title="Servicios"
  heading="Servicios de Valor para el Sector Agronómico"
  description="Llevamos la tecnología al campo para transformar datos en rentabilidad. Descubre nuestras herramientas diseñadas para la agricultura del futuro."
  variant="tools"
  layoutType="suspended"
  image="/images/herramientas/gps_antenna_tractor.png"
  heroSectionClass="hero-servicios-premium"
  bodySectionClass="page-body--herramientas"
>
  <div class="subpage-content">
    <section class="services-intro">
      <div class="services-intro__panel">
        <div class="services-intro__copy">
          <span class="section-eyebrow">Servicios especializados</span>
          <h2>Un mapa claro para entender qué servicio resuelve cada necesidad.</h2>
          <p>
            La página organiza nuestras capacidades en bloques fáciles de leer para
            que puedas identificar rápidamente qué herramienta encaja mejor con tu
            explotación, tu operativa y tus exigencias normativas.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="services-intro__signals">
          <div class="signal-card">
            <strong>Optimización</strong>
            <span>Mejora el uso de insumos, rutas y decisiones técnicas.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="signal-card">
            <strong>Trazabilidad</strong>
            <span>Documenta procesos y certifica actuaciones ante la administración.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="signal-card">
            <strong>Asistencia</strong>
            <span>Combina tecnología aplicada con acompañamiento agronómico experto.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services-catalog">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">Catálogo de valor</span>
        <h2>Servicios pensados para decisiones más precisas en campo.</h2>
        <p>
          Cada bloque resume de forma visual qué hace el servicio, por qué importa
          y dónde profundizar si quieres verlo con más detalle.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="services-main-grid">
        <article class="service-card-premium service-card-premium--featured glass">
          <div class="service-card__topline">
            <span class="service-card__index">01</span>
            <span class="service-card__tag">Dosis variable</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <img src="/images/herramientas/gps_antenna_tractor.png" alt="GPS Antenna on Tractor" width="56" height="56" />
          </div>
          <h3>Prescripción Digital</h3>
          <p>Optimiza el uso de insumos con mapas de dosis variable basados en vigor real. Ahorra hasta un 25% en fitosanitarios.</p>
          <div class="service-card__footer">
            <a href="/herramientas/prescripcion" class="service-link">Explorar Servicio</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card-premium glass">
          <div class="service-card__topline">
            <span class="service-card__index">02</span>
            <span class="service-card__tag">Cumplimiento nitratos</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13"></rect><polygon points="16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8"></polygon><circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"></circle><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"></circle></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Logística de Estiércoles</h3>
          <p>Control total de deyecciones ganaderas. Trazabilidad GPS avanzada y cumplimiento estricto del Decreto de Nitratos.</p>
          <div class="service-card__footer">
            <a href="/herramientas/estiercoles" class="service-link">Explorar Servicio</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card-premium glass">
          <div class="service-card__topline">
            <span class="service-card__index">03</span>
            <span class="service-card__tag">Control documental</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="1 6 1 22 8 18 16 22 23 18 23 2 16 6 8 2 1 6"></polygon><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="18"></line><line x1="16" y1="6" x2="16" y2="22"></line></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Trazabilidad GPS DARP</h3>
          <p>Certifica cada aplicación y transporte ante la administración. Informes automáticos de rutas y coberturas.</p>
          <div class="service-card__footer">
            <a href="/herramientas/trazabilidad" class="service-link">Explorar Servicio</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card-premium glass">
          <div class="service-card__topline">
            <span class="service-card__index">04</span>
            <span class="service-card__tag">Validación experta</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="8.5" cy="7" r="4"></circle><polyline points="17 11 19 13 23 9"></polyline></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Asesoramiento Técnico</h3>
          <p>Validación profesional de tratamientos y planes de abonado por ingenieros agrónomos expertos.</p>
          <div class="service-card__footer">
            <a href="/herramientas/asesoramiento" class="service-link">Explorar Servicio</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sustainability-highlight premium-benefits-box">
      <div class="highlight-content text-white">
        <span class="section-eyebrow section-eyebrow--light">Impacto transversal</span>
        <h2>Compromiso con la Sostenibilidad</h2>
        <p>Nuestras herramientas no solo mejoran tu rentabilidad, sino que reducen tu huella ambiental. Calculamos automáticamente el balance de nitrógeno y la eficiencia en el uso del agua para una agricultura regenerativa.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="highlight-box highlight-box--services">
      <h3>¿Dudas sobre por dónde empezar?</h3>
      <p>Nuestro equipo técnico te ayudará a identificar qué servicios aportarán mayor valor inmediato a tu explotación.</p>
      <a href="/contacto" class="cta-btn">Solicitar Diagnóstico Digital</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    :global(.page-hero.hero-servicios-premium) {
      min-height: 430px;
      padding-top: 12px !important;
      padding-bottom: 32px !important;
      overflow: hidden;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 18% 20%, rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.18), transparent 22%),
        linear-gradient(110deg, rgba(6, 14, 11, 0.82) 0%, rgba(6, 14, 11, 0.56) 48%, rgba(6, 14, 11, 0.22) 100%),
        #0B1A14 !important;
    }

    :global(.page-hero.hero-servicios-premium::before) {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 78% 28%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), transparent 18%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    :global(.hero-servicios-premium .page-hero__container) {
      z-index: 2;
    }

    :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended) {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.15fr) minmax(320px, 0.85fr);
      gap: 52px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended__content) {
      position: relative;
      padding: 34px 36px 30px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: rgba(7, 16, 13, 0.38);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px -42px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.48);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended__content::before) {
      content: "SERVICIOS";
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      padding: 7px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.14);
      border: 1px solid rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.22);
      color: #c6f7ec;
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    }

    :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended__content h1) {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5.2vw, 4.8rem);
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      max-width: 11ch;
    }

    :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended__content p) {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 56ch;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
    }

    :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended__image) {
      max-width: none;
      margin-left: 0;
      transform: none;
      border-radius: 32px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.18), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(8, 18, 14, 0.96), rgba(12, 27, 21, 0.92));
      box-shadow: 0 36px 80px -36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42);
      padding: 18px;
    }

    :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended__image img) {
      border-radius: 22px;
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 4.6;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    }

    :global(.page-body.page-body--herramientas) {
      padding-top: 30px !important;
      padding-bottom: 10px !important;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.08), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f7faf9 0%, #ffffff 24%, #f4faf7 100%);
    }

    .subpage-content {
      padding-bottom: 0 !important;
      margin-bottom: 0 !important;
    }

    .section-heading {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto 34px;
      text-align: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .section-eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 7px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.1);
      color: var(--color-turquoise-dark);
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .section-eyebrow--light {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .services-intro {
      margin-bottom: 42px;
    }

    .services-intro__panel {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.15fr) minmax(300px, 0.85fr);
      gap: 26px;
      padding: 34px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98), rgba(244, 250, 247, 0.96));
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 54px -36px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18);
    }

    .services-intro__copy h2 {
      margin: 14px 0 16px !important;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem) !important;
      line-height: 1.02;
    }

    .services-intro__copy p {
      margin: 0 !important;
      max-width: 60ch;
    }

    .services-intro__signals {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .signal-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px -28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.2);
    }

    .signal-card strong {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--color-slate-900);
    }

    .signal-card span {
      color: var(--color-slate-700);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .services-catalog {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .services-main-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 26px;
      margin-bottom: 64px;
    }

    .service-card-premium {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100%;
      padding: 32px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96), rgba(247, 251, 249, 0.94));
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 56px -38px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18);
      transition: transform 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease, border-color 0.35s ease;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .service-card-premium::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0 auto auto 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-turquoise), rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.12));
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .service-card-premium:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      border-color: rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.28);
      box-shadow: 0 28px 64px -36px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.24);
    }

    .service-card-premium--featured {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.12), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98), rgba(241, 249, 246, 0.96));
    }

    .service-card__topline {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .service-card__index {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.12);
      color: var(--color-turquoise-dark);
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .service-card__tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
      color: var(--color-slate-700);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .service-card__icon {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.1);
      color: var(--color-turquoise-dark);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.12);
    }

    .service-card__icon img {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .service-card-premium h3 {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .service-card-premium p {
      margin-bottom: 0 !important;
      max-width: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.72;
    }

    .service-card__footer {
      margin-top: auto;
      padding-top: 22px;
    }

    .service-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      color: var(--color-turquoise-dark);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .service-link::after {
      content: "→";
      transition: transform 0.25s ease;
    }

    .service-card-premium:hover .service-link::after {
      transform: translateX(4px);
    }

    .sustainability-highlight {
      padding: 84px 44px;
      border-radius: 34px;
      margin: 0 0 56px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .premium-benefits-box {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.14), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(145deg, #0B1A14 0%, #163127 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.3);
      box-shadow: 0 40px 100px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }

    .highlight-content {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 860px;
    }

    .highlight-content h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4.5vw, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 850;
      margin: 18px 0 20px !important;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .highlight-content p {
      font-size: 1.14rem;
      line-height: 1.82;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto !important;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .text-white {
      color: white !important;
    }

    .highlight-box--services {
      margin: 0 !important;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended) {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended__content h1) {
        max-width: none;
      }

      .services-intro__panel {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .services-main-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      :global(.page-hero.hero-servicios-premium) {
        min-height: auto;
        padding-top: 0 !important;
        padding-bottom: 30px !important;
      }

      :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended) {
        gap: 26px;
      }

      :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended__content) {
        padding: 24px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended__content h1) {
        max-width: none;
      }

      :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended__content p) {
        max-width: none;
      }

      :global(.hero-servicios-premium .hero-suspended__image) {
        padding: 14px;
      }

      :global(.page-body.page-body--herramientas) {
        padding-top: 18px !important;
        padding-bottom: 20px !important;
      }

      .services-intro {
        margin-bottom: 34px;
      }

      .services-intro__panel {
        padding: 24px 20px;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .services-intro__copy,
      .section-heading {
        text-align: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .services-main-grid {
        gap: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .service-card-premium {
        padding: 24px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .service-card__topline {
        width: 100%;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .service-card__footer {
        width: 100%;
        padding-top: 18px;
      }

      .service-link {
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .sustainability-highlight {
        padding: 42px 20px;
        margin-bottom: 36px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</TestPage>
